se-reverra_key2: Ab aapne HTML aur CSS ka Beginner course khatam kar liya hai. Ab aap apni pasand ki koi bhi ek website chun kar HTML aur CSS use kar kar bana sakte ho.
se-reverra_key3: Yeh website bana kar, aap aas paas sabko dikhao, aur unse suggestions lo ki aap kaise isse behtar bana sakte ho.
se-reverra_key4: Yeh `code` aap sambhaal kar rakhna, aage aapka **CV** yaani **Curriculum Vitae** banate waqt kaafi kaam aayega.
se-reverra_key6: Aap page jis website ka clone hai, bilkul uske jaisa dikhna chahiye. Issi tarah se aapki practice theek tarah se hogi.
